And so we talk about\nthat all the time.
And I think that fair\nhousing is at its heart
about economic mobility\nbecause Shaun often
said housing determines\nso many things.
Where your house is\ndetermines what school system
you go to, what\njobs are accessible,
whether you can spend\ntime out on the streets
because they're\nsafe or not safe.
And if your house is not in a\nplace where those amenities are
